95/poem-NhBWMA-84xXu9nrwDwPiHA">Hồ thành hoài cổ - 胡城懷古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Th%C3%BAc-Tr%E1%BB%B1c/author-0CTnEDQGEKViETWZXrhgww">Phan Thúc Trực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/K%C3%ADnh-k%C3%BD-t%E1%BB%99c-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-th%E1%BA%ADp-b%C3%A1t-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n/poem-XybYZnhDZgnjnGDKwsdg8Q">Kính ký tộc đệ Đường thập bát sứ quân - 敬寄族弟唐十八使君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Anh-T%C3%B4ng/K%C3%BD-Ph%E1%BB%95-Tu%E1%BB%87-t%C3%B4n-gi%E1%BA%A3-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-YamuqEbJfL3p9w18rgqnlQ">Ký Phổ Tuệ tôn giả kỳ 1 - 寄普慧尊者其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Anh-T%C3%B4ng/author-YFBCcaKGsPA7uILcS-B8_Q">Trần Anh Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Ph%C3%B3ng-ng%C3%B4n-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-j1NsF-L-kuqg8ZJRLu1Sfw">Phóng ngôn kỳ 3 - 放言其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br></div>	</div>
